  <brief_title>Metformin for Treatment Antipsychotic Induced Amenorrhea in Female Schizophrenic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Metformin for Treatment Antipsychotic Induced Amenorrhea in Female Schizophrenic Patients: a Double Blind, Placebo-controlled Study</official_title>
