  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Antipsychotics such as risperidone could induce amenorrhea in schizophrenic patients. The
      investigators conducted a randomized, placebo-controlled study to test the efficacy of
      metformin for antipsychotic induced amenorrhea in schizophrenia patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
